I Do is the ninth episode of the twelfth season of ER, and the two hundred fifty-fourth episode overall.

Starring: Goran Visnjic (Dr. Luka Kovac), Maura Tierney (Dr. Abby Lockhart), Mekhi Phifer (Dr. Gregory Pratt), Parminder Nagra (Dr. Neela Rasgotra), Linda Cardellini (Nurse Samantha Taggart), Shane West (Dr. Ray Barnett), Scott Grimes (Dr. Archie Morris)

and Laura Innes (Dr. Kerry Weaver)

Special Guest Stars: John Leguizamo (Dr. Victor Clemente), Leland Orser (Dr. Lucien Dubenko)

and Sharif Atkins (Michael Gallant),

Plot Overview

Neela and Gallant decide to get married; Luka becomes the new chief of the ER and faces tension with Clemente; Sam tries to convince a mother to allow treatment for her young HIV-positive son.
